{"id":577312,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/01/【图说天朝】没字的书那还叫书吗/","date":"2018-01-26T08:14:55Z","modified":"2018-01-26T08:14:55Z","title":"【图说天朝】没字的书那还叫书吗","content":"<p>@还是一碗泡面：朋友圈看到一组评论截图，国内绘本作者真苦啊！</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/6aa54acfly1fnty9li3t4j20u00ik773.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-577313\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/6aa54acfly1fnty9li3t4j20u00ik773.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"309\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/6aa54acfly1fnty9li3t4j20u00ik773.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/6aa54acfly1fnty9li3t4j20u00ik773-300x186.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/6aa54acfly1fnty9li3t4j20u00ik773-80x48.jpg 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a> <a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/6aa54acfly1fnty9lwrrfj20ri0qowhm.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-577314\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/6aa54acfly1fnty9lwrrfj20ri0qowhm.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"485\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/6aa54acfly1fnty9lwrrfj20ri0qowhm.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/6aa54acfly1fnty9lwrrfj20ri0qowhm-300x291.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a> <a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/6aa54acfly1fnty9mhktij20sv0qo439.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-577315\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/6aa54acfly1fnty9mhktij20sv0qo439.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"462\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/6aa54acfly1fnty9mhktij20sv0qo439.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/6aa54acfly1fnty9mhktij20sv0qo439-300x277.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a> <a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/6aa54acfly1fnty9mxtbkj20qo10pgt8.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-577316\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/6aa54acfly1fnty9mxtbkj20qo10pgt8.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"688\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/6aa54acfly1fnty9mxtbkj20qo10pgt8.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/6aa54acfly1fnty9mxtbkj20qo10pgt8-218x300.jpg 218w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a> <a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/6aa54acfly1fnty9nerp7j20qo0syjut.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-577317\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/6aa54acfly1fnty9nerp7j20qo0syjut.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"543\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/6aa54acfly1fnty9nerp7j20qo0syjut.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/6aa54acfly1fnty9nerp7j20qo0syjut-276x300.jpg 276w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a> <a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/6aa54acfly1fnty9nu8k4j20qo0u3790.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-577318\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/6aa54acfly1fnty9nu8k4j20qo0u3790.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"564\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/6aa54acfly1fnty9nu8k4j20qo0u3790.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/6aa54acfly1fnty9nu8k4j20qo0u3790-266x300.jpg 266w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>以下为数字时代编辑摘自部分网友评论：</strong></p>\n<p>@奶爸高律师：哎…部分网民依旧处于只能认字的初级阶段</p>\n<p>@RC的微脖儿：群众普遍认为给得多=好，同理可见各种装修、服装、平面设计……</p>\n<p>@小时候我可长啦：那去买新华字典啊！字多又厚实。</p>\n<p>@雷逍妖：这还不是最惨的，我之前去买字帖，《祭侄文稿》底下有人评论：”什么质量还做字帖，怎么涂涂改改划得这么脏！”我他妈哪知道为啥，你问颜真卿去。</p>\n<p>@溜溜的云的小屋：所以这就是每次请家长带绘本到幼儿园来结果买一本超多字的故事来的原因。殊不知让幼儿多从画面去明白故事内容比直接从字面去了解更重要。</p>\n<p>@辣手老军医豆包：许多人买书跟买白菜是同一个心理，便宜量又大才好</p>\n<p>@舒挽歌：国内非艺术从业者的艺术修养，基本是没有的……反正从初中起就没有什么美术课了。</p>\n<p>@_A九_：小孩没字也能看懂书在说什么，这些成年人离了文字反而是文盲似的看不懂。</p>\n<p>@刘鑫今天炸了吗：国内就这样 学艺术的心凉凉</p>\n<p>@不梁猫：我气愤得只想踢爆他们脑袋。</p>\n<p>@喵酱_nana：绘本都不懂吗</p>\n<p>@朕是一茗：我觉得至少应该尊重下别人的劳动成果</p>\n<p>@抖S趙小漁：不奇怪，很多人只停留在认字阶段，不懂更高层次的审美。</p>\n<p><strong>相关阅读：</strong></p>\n<p><a title=\"【CDTV】文昭 | 运动来时大封网 《1984》、袁腾飞和白雪公主\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/01/%e3%80%90cdtv%e3%80%91%e6%96%87%e6%98%ad-%e8%bf%90%e5%8a%a8%e6%9d%a5%e6%97%b6%e5%a4%a7%e5%b0%81%e7%bd%91-%e3%80%8a1984%e3%80%8b%e3%80%81%e8%a2%81%e8%85%be%e9%a3%9e%e5%92%8c%e7%99%bd%e9%9b%aa/\">【CDTV】文昭 | 运动来时大封网 《1984》、袁腾飞和白雪公主</a></p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18270,18269,10466,21627],"tags":[29744,28069,16868,33842,33841,16222]}